<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <% include ../partials/head %>
  <% include ../partials/css %>
  <script src="scripts/participate.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
  <style>
    #YTplayer {
      max-width: 513px;
      max-height: 288.6px;
    }
    .content {
      max-width: 513px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 500px) {
      #YTplayer {
        max-width: 352px;
        max-height: 200px;
      }
      .content {
        max-width: 352px;
      }
    }

    @media (min-width: 992px) {
      #YTplayer {
        max-width: 673px;
        max-height: 378.6px;
      }
      .content {
        max-width: 673px;
      }
    }

    @media (min-width: 1200px) {
      #YTplayer {
        max-width: 833px;
        max-height: 468.6px;
      }
      .content {
        max-width: 833px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <%- include('../partials/header-'.concat(auth?'':'no').concat('auth')) %>
  </header>
  <main>
    <div style="text-align:center; margin: 0 auto;"><div id="YTplayer"></div></div>
    <div class="container content">
      <h1>How to participate</h1>
      <div id='hiddenp' style='display: none;'>
        <p><b>When you click the button below, you will be directed to sign up/log in (if you haven't done so yet), followed by the practice session.</b></p>
        
        <div id="button-container" style="margin: 0 auto; text-align:center;">
          <a style="text-decoration:none;" href="/login"><button id="continue">Continue</button></a><br>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>We need your help to understand the environmental health of the Gowanus Canal. All you need to do is examine the images taken by our aquatic robot, identify anything that you thinkis an <b> object of interest</b>, and label it. This makes you a citizen scientist! <br><br> To Learn more about the Gowanus Canal and our project, please watch the video above. </p> 
  </main>
  <footer>
    <% include ../partials/footer %>
  </footer>
  <last>
    <% include ../partials/scripts %>
  </last>
</body>
</html>